# 🤖 Artificial Intelligence

## 📖 Overview

This section contains my Artificial Intelligence (AI) learning journey, concepts, implementations, and projects. The goal of this repository is to build a strong foundation in AI by understanding core principles, implementing algorithms, and developing practical applications.

Artificial Intelligence enables machines to simulate human intelligence, including learning, reasoning, problem-solving, decision-making, and pattern recognition. This repository serves as a structured roadmap covering theoretical concepts and hands-on projects.

